name: Donna Fore
what_you_do: Donna Fore is currently a business owner and Advisor with Mutual of Omaha in Central Texas.
social_proof: Retired military officer having served her country for over 30 years in the United States Air Force. She served at The Pentagon and is a survivor of the terrorist attacks conducted on September 11th, 2001.
business_focus: Donna Fore is a retired military officer who now owns an insurance services business with Mutual of Omaha in Central Texas.
